{"tid":980202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金沙賭場男子企跳消防局現正處理","createTime":"2019-01-13T10:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T12:44:51.000Z","uid":171658,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9c225fbc3b4d1e05dc2347b012a8927325d9de","tid":980202,"uid":171658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:42:51.000Z","msg":"金沙賭場男子企跳 消防局現正處理<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190110/mobile/bkn-20190110220458239-0110_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190110%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190110220458239-0110_00822_001.html&d=O0Ck5FDcW8taR8KUalswukbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a2614703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190110/mobile/bkn-20190110220458239-0110_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=O0Ck5FDcW8taR8KUalswukbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a68ed01b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】澳門金沙酒店內有人企跳。網上今日(10日)流傳短片，一名男子站在該酒店賭場內閣樓走廊的欄杆外，雙手扶着半透明玻璃疑企跳，不停四處張望。有保安人員一度嘗試說服該男子返回走廊，但未能成功，暫時未知其企跳原因。<br />\n<br />\n消防局晚上證實事件，指澳門蒙地卡羅前地金沙酒店發生一宗企跳事件，現在處理當中。"},{"pid":"aaccd373f869d95a28af564265d732491c0bac70","tid":980202,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"有賭未為輸呀<br />\n落黎拉多次老虎機<br />\n分分鐘jackpot就係你"},{"pid":"14e0b9374cb0ea0a83e0499169dd353987e04a2e","tid":980202,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:44:48.000Z","msg":"企你老母跳，企圖跳樓就企圖跳樓，咪撚嘢企跳，屌你老母百份"},{"pid":"586634809daed9adb2a73811f49d8faf83aa2104","tid":980202,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"10日"},{"pid":"b27c451324a19b8bfd117ef2f11d0af3791b5055","tid":980202,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"舊葡京賭客表示以前見唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s